---
---

<section class="phi" aria-label="Philosophy">
  <div class="phi__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="frame">
    <div class="phi__inner">

      <div class="phi__left reveal">
        <span class="t-label t-label--warm">The work</span>
      </div>

      <div class="phi__right">
        <p class="phi__statement reveal d1">
          There is a quality of attention that most people have never experienced in their own lives.
        </p>
        <p class="phi__body reveal d2">
          Not insight. Not knowledge. Something that happens in the body, in real time, in the presence
          of difficulty or beauty or silence. The retreats, the mountain expeditions, the mentorship —
          they are all attempts to create the conditions for that quality to emerge.
        </p>
        <p class="phi__attribution reveal d3">
          <span class="t-label t-label--warm">Yakov Rajuna</span>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .phi {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--atm-phi);
    padding-block: clamp(100px, 16svh, 220px);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .phi__bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 55% at 100% 0%,   rgba(200,155,90,0.20), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 0%   100%, rgba(214,178,112,0.12), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .phi__inner {
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 8vw, 120px);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .phi__left { padding-top: 8px; }

  .phi__statement {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.2vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--earth);
    margin: 0 0 var(--s-7);
    max-width: 22ch;
    font-optical-sizing: auto;
  }

  .phi__body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--fg-soft);
    margin: 0 0 var(--s-6);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  .phi__attribution { margin: 0; }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .phi__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s-6); }
  }
</style>
